	<!-- Homepage Product Schema -->
    <script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org/","@type":"Product","name":"Window World of Jersey Coast","image":"https://www.jerseycoastwindows.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/window-world-logo.png","description":"Window World of the Jersey Coast is the leading provider of premium vinyl replacement windows,siding,and doors throughout the Greater NJ area.","brand":{"@type":"Brand","name":"Window World of Jersey Coast"},"aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":"4.9","bestRating":"5","worstRating":"1","ratingCount":"626"},"review":[{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I had the delightful opportunity to work with Window World on three impactful projects in my home:replacing the aging windows in my basement,installing a stylish new sliding door,and updating all twelve windows throughout the house.\n\nFrom the very first point of contact with Window World,I was struck by the exceptional level of service they provided. The sales agent,Ken S.,was not only knowledgeable but also keenly attentive,taking the time to grasp my specific needs and preferences. He expertly navigated me through an array of window styles and door options,sharing comprehensive details about energy efficiency,materials,and design choices. This bespoke approach instilled a sense of confidence in my decisions,making the entire process feel personalized and focused on my satisfaction.\n\nAfter placing my order,Window World promptly informed me about the anticipated installation timeline. I genuinely appreciated the regular updates they provided,which kept me well-informed about the approximate date for installation\u2014it was reassuring to see that everything was executed right on schedule. This transparent communication allowed me to prepare my home effectively and coordinate my schedule around the installation.\n\nOn the day of the installation,the crew arrived punctually at the agreed-upon time,exuding professionalism from the moment they set foot on my property. They were fully equipped and ready to tackle the tasks at hand. I was particularly taken by their meticulous approach; they carefully dismantled the old windows and sliding door,ensuring that my home sustained no damage throughout the process.\n\nOne aspect that particularly left an impression on me was their unwavering dedication to cleanliness. After completing the installation,the crew made a concerted effort to leave my home in pristine condition. Each of my belongings was treated with the utmost care,and they took the time to clean up every scrap and dust particle,ensuring that their work left no trace behind\u2014a testament to their professionalism.\n\nIf you're considering enhancing your home with a new sliding door,basement windows,or any other window replacements,I wholeheartedly recommend Window World. Their pricing stands out as incredibly competitive compared to many other window companies,all while offering high-quality products that are backed by a transferable lifetime warranty. This warranty is a remarkable selling point,as it can be transferred to new homeowners,adding immense value if you ever decide to sell your property.\n\nMoreover,their customer service is truly exceptional; any questions or concerns I had were addressed promptly and courteously,showing their commitment to client satisfaction. Overall,my experience was thoroughly rewarding,and I wouldn't hesitate to recommend Window World to anyone in need of window or door replacements. Keep up the fantastic work,Window World! I eagerly look forward to returning for my next home improvement project.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Andrew Kibet"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Excellent experience from the sales team to customer service to installers. The door replacement I received was affordable with valuable financing option. The customer service team kept me updated and communicated with me throughout the entire process which was very appreciated. The installers were top-notch they took their time and transformed our old door which was on its last leg and turned it into a beautiful new front door. We could not be happier and will definitely be looking to replace our side door and windows with this company due to the service and workmanship that they provided.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Sean Reeves"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Had all of my windows replaced by window world recently. Couldn\u2019t be happier with the job they did. All done in one day with a team of three hard working and friendly individuals. The framing and woodwork came out beautiful. It has made my home feel bright and clean. And for the first time in years I can see clearly through my beautiful windows! Thank you to your fabulous team,from installers,sales,and the office team. You made it so very easy for me during the entire process.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Kim Hickey"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I have used Window World a couple of years ago to replace my windows. They did such a good job. I called them back to do my siding,and I must say the job from start to finish was a success. I completely recommend Window World 100%.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Clarence Ross"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We\u2019re 100% satisfied with our new windows from Window World! Our sales rep,Jack,was extremely helpful and knowledgeable\u2014he made the whole process effortless. We noticed a big difference when getting quotes,and it was a no-brainer to go with Window World after meeting with him. The installation was fast,clean,and made a huge difference in our home\u2019s heating right away. The house looks completely refreshed from the outside. Highly recommend!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Doris Amenyo"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The entire experience with Window World (WW) was wonderful! We had our entry door replaced. The salesperson,Greg,was very knowledgeable and helpful with options that would meet our needs. Once we decided to go with WW,they made the process with getting the approval from our HOA seamless. The door was delivered on time and we were able to get the installation scheduled quickly. The installers did a great job! They were on time and professional. Once the work was complete they made sure we were happy with the results. I highly recommend Window World!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Denecia Quander"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I am incredibly happy to have worked with Window World. Their team did an outstanding job \u2014 they were clean,friendly,professional,and the materials used are of excellent quality. The sliding doors and windows they installed are fantastic and have transformed my home.\n\nThe price was very affordable,especially considering I haven\u2019t replaced my windows and doors in over 25 years. The management team was honest,helpful,and attentive throughout the process. The technicians who installed the windows were very professional and polite,making the experience smooth and pleasant.\n\nI\u2019m truly satisfied with the service and product. Thank you very much! I highly recommend Window World to anyone looking for quality windows and doors at a great price.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"maryann H"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We had a great experience with this company. No hassle free quote,they did not demand both homeowners to be present unlike other companies. We had a drafty bow window replaced with a bay. It is beautiful. Even had it installed earlier than expected.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Maureen Corby"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World did a fantastic job installing our replacement windows. We are extremely happy with the product and everyone we dealt with was professional and courteous. It was a very good experience from top to bottom.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"carol spatz"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The entire process was a great experience. The company worked with me to accommodate my needs. I couldn\u2019t say enough positive things about the men that installed my windows. They were polite,respectful and genuinely cared about doing an awesome job. I would absolutely recommend using Window World,and I will add this is an honest biased free review.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Janet K"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Great experience. This company is friendly,communicative and transparent. The quality of the windows and install are very good so far. I had 2 quotes and the other company offered wild preliminary prices to alarm you and then offered many \"end of year discounts\". Competitor also wanted 5-star review up front,prior to install,in order to get additional discounts - red flag. Window world does none of that and offers a good straightforward service. Highly recommend.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Bekim Becaj"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"My prior window( a bowed crank open window) and door in my dinning room were,ugh,uninspiring. Window World came out and showed me the light,I'm not kidding it totally transformed my kitchen/dining room. So Thank You Window World for fixing my windows and doors and showing me the light.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Jon Douglas"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window world is the best company from my quoting experience. Afford price,very comprehensive descriptions of service,promising appointments and installation. They made everything so easy and convenient. I would recommend window world to everyone who\u2019s looking for great and affordable service","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Xiaona Bala-Moon"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World of Jersey Coast from Edison did an excellent job.\n\nSales Rep:John was great.\n\nOwner and Manager:They did a great job by always staying in touch. They were patient,attentive,respectful,and flexible to our requests. We liked the job well done and were originally hesitant to start this large project,thinking something might definitely go wrong when changing all 36 windows and a door. However,I was assured that the installation team managed by Jose would do a great job.\nThey didn't lie.\n\nService and Installation Team:The job and service we received were beyond great,I mean it. I certainly recommend their service. I especially want to thank Jose and his team of installers. They truly were something special. I haven't seen this type of excellence for some time.\n\nThanks!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"VA"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World provided me with a great window shopping experience. After quoting with three other companies,I was disappointed and overwhelmed with the extremely high prices the other companies were providing. My sales rep John came in and guaranteed that I would be satisfied after my appointment with him and he was right! Window World's prices are extremely competitive (other companies were 3x's the price) and financing was super easy. They advised my windows would arrive in three weeks and they arrived in two weeks. They scheduled my installation for a few days after the windows arrived. The installers came in on time,the installation took 8 hours and everything was left clean. The windows look amazing and I will definitely be recommending Window World to my friends and family.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Jennifer Romero"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I recently had two windows installed at my townhouse by Window World. This is my second time using them,and I\u2019d gladly recommend them. The salesperson was great\u2014gave me all the facts quickly without any hassle. The installation team was on time,did excellent work,cleaned up after themselves,and even showed me how to use the new windows. Very professional experience all around.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Cecilia Vazquez"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Our sales person was very informative and respectful to our concern and needs. The installation team did a great job and was very efficient. They cleaned up everything when they were done. Windows in out basement look amazing.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Nicholas Tarquinio"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Like anybody else,I shopped around to get the best value for my money. I had 10 windows needed to be replaced and by far Window World stood out. Great quality windows and truly transparent. Would highly recommend if you\u2019re looking to get your windows replaced.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Shiv Patel"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Loving my new windows from Window World of Jersey Coast! Reasonable pricing,the girls in the office were helpful with any questions I had. The install crew were very clean and respectful. Overall very satisfied with Window World,highly recommend! Can not wait for my new Entry Doors and Storms Doors to arrive and make my home look beautiful!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Alexis Taormina"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We purchased replacement windows and an exterior door. Window World was recommended to us by two different neighbors and we have been extremely happy. The salesman was not pushy,their pricing was better than two other estimates and their installers had 9 windows replaced within 6 hours. One window seemed to stick and they came out to inspect quickly. The window was adjusted when they came back to install the door. Installing the door took about 3 hours and they were meticulous in making sure it was completely level with no spaces around the door. We have recommended Window World of Jersey Coast to others as we received many compliments on how nice our replacement windows and door look. We highly recommend Window World of Jersey Coast.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"barbara sinatra"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Great job! Great prices and I have used this company before so I saved them for last to compare!! All the other companies were double the price,did not include a bay window nor new entry door with storm door!!! Windows are lightly tinted,and have lifetime warranty!!! Got more for my money And feel this company has been honest and trustworthy!! Recommend it to all my friends!!!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Frances Sohl"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window world was professional and wonderful to work with from the initial consultation all the way through installation. Jack,our sales person explained all of the details and made the process very easy. Installers were on time and installed all of our windows in one day. They cleaned so well and there was minimal dust. I would highly recommend window world.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Urmilla"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"George led the work crew of window world. He conducted himself in a professional manner throughout the entire project,which was 1 1/2 days. I had a lot of windows. All the men that worked with him were courteous,professional and worked hard! They took away all the old windows and did a great job of cleaning up\u2026inside and out. They are all to be commended. You cannot go wrong if you choose Window World for your next windows.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Teresa Cattanach"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We recently had an entry door installed by Window World of Jersey Coast. It was a pleasure to work with our salesperson,John Gary. He was very informative and explained all the options and warranties. The office staff kept in contact with us to let us know that our door was ordered and the approximate installation date. The door was installed on time as scheduled. We were very impressed with the installation crew:Frank,Adrien and Brian. They had a few challenges but they worked very hard to make sure that the installation was perfect. The door is exactly what we hoped for. I would give Window World my highest recommendation,they did an excellent job for us.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Lori Uffer"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Salesman John was excellent. He wasn't pushy and very patiently answered all my questions whenever I interrupted him. He also gave a formative and interesting presentation.\n\nMy double-hung replacement windows are much better from the start than the Home Depot replacements ever were. I don't have the old windows to compare,but the sashes seem narrower giving more square inches of glass.\n\nThe icing on the cake was since the windows were installed from outside,the aluminum framing around the outside of each window was replaced and the workmanship was A+. I ordered vinyl or PVC wrapping and it's so much nicer than the aluminum that was installed with the vinyl siding. I will be looking into having all my other windows wrapped the same way and hopefully they'll the job.\n\nThe 2 workers were well trained and did fantastic work with every aspect of the installation.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Joe Shmoe"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The whole transaction was very smooth. I loved the communication using texting and confirmation on each step. The contractor completed the job just one day and cleaned very well. I am very happy to use the window world to replace my windows. Definitely will recommend window world to my friends and neighbors.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Jing Gao"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Our agent John was awesome. He was very knowledgeable and answered all our questions to make us feel comfortable. The gentleman who came to replace our windows were efficient,took their time and worked hard. Everyone working at window world was a big help and very nice from start to finish. Recommend them 100%","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"LG"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World made the process of replacing my windows so easy. From the no-pressure sales pitch,helping out with getting my home owners association the documents they needed,to keeping me updated with the order status. The seven windows of my townhouse were installed in less than a day and the two installers cleaned up before they left. Everyone I encountered at the company was friendly and pleasant to work with. And most importantly,my windows look great!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Melissa F"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I needed two windows replaced in my home. I called Window World because of all the wonderful reviews. Window World did not disappoint! Every person I dealt with from start to finish was courteous,professional and knowledgeable. I love my windows so much! They look beautiful and the quality definitely shows! Thank you to the amazing team at Window World for your exceptional service and making me happy!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Shirley Rodriguez"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Professional,kind,caring and respectful from beginning to end!! We got an insane quote from Renewal by Anderson,was recommended window world from a neighbor and several others,pricing is extremely reasonable and they truly work with you! Our Salesman John was great,all of the ladies who followed up with us on appointments and updates were so nice,and the guys who came to install were very clean and respectful. We are very happy,thank you guys so much!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Paige Kuhlmann"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Painless experience. Greg,our sales rep was great. After reception other quotes from other well known window retailers,Greg's quote was the best. We had our new windows in 3 weeks:installed in just about 3 hours. We will be buying more. Our house just had a nice makeover\nHighly recommend","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Judith Leon"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Our entire experience with Window World was extremely positive,starting from sales,to follow-up and scheduling,to the installation. All personnel were quick,efficient,polite and professional. We recommend them highly","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"David Sardar"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The recent work performed (windows) at our home was done professionally,and efficiently. The guys did a great job! The final outcome was very much to our liking. We were very pleased and very satisfied with Window World and their support!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"louis serio"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Great job done by Window World. Professional and courteous. My new patio doors look fantastic!!! Highly recommend. Thank you Window World!!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Judie Felder"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The process was seamless. From 1st sales appointment with Jack,to measurement and installation took 2 weeks. About to do doors with Jack as well.Thanks so much!!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Jason Kessler"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Love my new window. The salesman Jack was awesome!! The crew was early,neat and professional. When done the only complaint I had was this new beautiful window made my other windows look old. Haha I highly recommend Window World. Thank you!!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Toni Ott"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World provided an all over excellent Service from Estimate to ordering and Installing our Salesman was very knowledgeable of His Products Installers were very Knowledgeable,Respectful,quick and worked Neatly and Cleaned up all areas","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Jacqueline Barowski"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I have 32 year old windows that needed to be replaced. I finally decided this is the year. I called around for quotes,and although Window World was a little higher,it was 1000% worth it. From start to finish the communication was constant. From the sales person to measure,to install took about 5 weeks and the windows are made to order. Customer service let you know the status every step of the way. The windows are beautiful. I highly recommend them.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Ellen K"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Great service,Arrived promptly for the scheduled appointment. Workers were polite and very neat. Completed the job to our satisfaction. Would certainly use This company for another project","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"4"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Joan Blake"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Gary our salesman was Top Notch knew his product explained everything to us was very nice we are very happy with our Windows how they came out and the installers were very nice very efficient cleaned up everything and did impeccable work","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Patricia Corr"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World did a great job on my 90 year old house. From start to finish we are happy!\nTony was great and we are going to use him again in the future.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Jeff Killian"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Process was smooth,from initial in home sales meeting to actual installation. Not the cheapest prices and certainly not the most expensive. All my concerns were addressed promptly. I can recommend this business based on my personal experience. I haven\u2019t needed to use the warranty,but by far the best warranty in writing that I\u2019ve seen on replacement windows.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Michael Bogart"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window world of jersey coast was great. Dan our salesman was knowledgeable. Price beat comparable competitors. Windows were custom made and installed within a month. They installed 20 windows in one day,no issues with installation. Looks great.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"HOCH'S LANDSCAPING"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Very professional. Attentive. Installers were courteous and hard working. Office personnel were very responsive.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Gail Stevancsecz"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We had work done three weeks ago. We got new windows,siding and gutters. The team came early and worked hard the entire time. It was below freezing and even snowed one day and they were still outside working hard. The work they did was amazing. You can feel the house is warmer and the outside noise is quieter. We would recommend them to anyone looking for new siding and new windows","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Courtney DeWitt"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"There were multiple locks on my windows where the plastic casing was splitting or completely cracked and broken. Kelly was very kind and scheduled a technician to come out and replace the broken locks. Labi ( not sure of the spelling of his name) replaced all the broken locks. He is a wonderful asset to Wonder Windows. I am completely satisfied with the quick response and professional help. Thank you.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Wen Zim"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I was referred to Window World by a neighbor who replaced most of the windows at his home a couple of years back. Reached out to Window World to get a free estimate and got a very quick response. Greg Rios from Window World came by home to provide an estimate,and he was really good. Generally,you envision sales people as being too pushy,but Greg was really nice and was very quick to respond to follow-up questions after his visit.\n\nWe had initially thought of replacing just 5 windows,but then,with the good deal aling with 1 yr payment plan they offered,ended up going with replacing 15 windows.\n\nDue to demand,it took like a month before the new windows were ready for the crew to come and replace our windows. The crew led by Romiro did their job neatly and really quickly. I was surprised they were able to replace all 15 windows in one day.\n\nWindow World also called after the installation to check if everything went well.\n\nSo far I am really happy with their service.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Anandbabu Adimala"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I highly recommend Window World,they have done windows for me,installed two doors just recently,and I have nothing negative to say about them. The workers are excellent.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Alina Fiallo"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We recently purchased an older home and needed to replace several windows.\nWe chose Window World based on their window quality and their pricing.\nAnd we\u2019re so glad we did!\nFrom the salesman to the office admin everyone we dealt with was kind,helpful and knowledgeable.\nOn our install day the installers arrived on time and went right to work.\nThey were very professional and very neat!\nWe highly recommend Window World and look forward to working with them again in the future.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Melanie Sullivan"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We\u2019ve Erika Ed every window in our home. Totally satisfied. Easy to clean and the guarantee is amazing","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Serina Cata"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Frank and his team did amazing job in installing new and replacing old windows including framework for my house !! I would highly recommend Windows world to friends and family !","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Bhavin Chokshi"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World came highly recommended via the app for my condo association. I read the Google reviews which were great as well! The process from beginning to end was such a pleasant one. Everyone was informative,helpful,transparent,and polite. They communicate with you at every step of the way. Installation was well done and efficient. I am a very satisfied customer. I love my new beautiful windows!!!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Cris Carkhuff"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Great product reasonable price. Installers were very neat,cleaned up all debris and explained widow operation. Highly recommend.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Joe Ditchkus"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Installers arrived early and wasted no time getting into project,finished in good time and cleaned up nicely,job well done. Over the past few years I\u2019ve had all windows in house renewed,\nWindow World was the installer,thanks !","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"john kishel"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Very nicely done,very professional. Cleaned the entire area afterwards,window were installed perfectly. All the workers were knowledgeable and did a great job.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Nancy Hahn"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"These guys are truly the best! I\u2019ve been using window world for over a decade for commercial and residential. They are done replacement windows,new window installs,new siding and roofing for me. Their work is always top notch and fairly priced.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Will Proetta"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Had a garden window replaced. All the way through the process of being in the showroom to measurements being taken to the install was a wonderful experience. The product is high quality as well as all the staff. Would definitely recommend them.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Jill Brown"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We had a very peasant experience in having our new windows installed by Window World. There were some unforeseen issues that they handled perfectly. We are very happy with our new windows.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Linda Barnes"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Great service,from the first representative (salesman) to the man that came to measure the spaces and the installers. We are so happy with the windows.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Elizabeth Pinella"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The quality of work here was a highlight for me. Also their ability to explain what they were doing and why. We had some amendments during the job and they were extremely flexible and cooperative. We had a smaller error in the panes that they delivered with the grids. A quick conversation with the owners and they made it all right. The guys did pretty good job on clean up too considering there was snow on the ground. We could not be happier with the work that was done and the prices we paid for it. I would recommend this company for window and/or siding install with the highest conviction.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Mike Smith"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Gave a very good price for the work needed. Came on time,when finished with the work they cleaned up & you couldn\u2019t tell they were there. The whole experience.was GREAT!! Would recommend Window World to anybody looking for their type of service . Rimo the salesman is very easy to deal with. He\u2019s the best.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"craig cabarle"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Once again a truly excellent service. The crew was wonderful,they are very careful of your property,they work non stop and everything is cleaned up when they are finished. I am sad I didn't take a before picture of the sliding glass door because the work both inside and out is amazing no one will believe what a difference this made. Another great experience starting with the planning and the measuring and the finished project. Also the finished woodwork inside is gorgeous and the finished outside is amazing. Great job thank you so much.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Marian Stamatis"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Had 3 vinyl windows replaced,that were hard to open. New windows open with ease and outside trim looks great.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Richard Bornemann"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"From the initial consultation with Doris,throughout the scheduling and installation process,Window World was a pleasure to work with. Our new sliders are beautiful and the extra care that went into our tricky interior molding did not go unnoticed. I would,and have,recommended Window World to friends and family!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Courtney Salmon"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Beautiful simple windows,sturdy,quickly installed. Will be buying 2 to 3 more come Spring","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"dldd4198"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I had 9 windows replaced and I am very satisfied with the quality of the product as well as the efficiency of the installers. They arrived on time finished the job in five hours and left the work area outside my home completely clear of all materials.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Mary Fause"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World recently replaced all windows at my house and I am very satisfied with the entire engagement. I highly recommend Window World to anyone looking to replace their windows!\n\nFirst of all,their salesmen are nothing like the 'sales gangsters' you see elsewhere with the windows and solar companies. Jack Perito went over all aspects of the new windows,why their windows and installation practices sets them apart from competitors and was very friendly and respectful throughout. He wasn't aggressive,understood and respected my decision making process.\n\nOnce I decided to go ahead with them,Madison from the office provided me a reasonable ETA for when windows would be ready for install. I ordered during the 2024 year-end and was told to expect installation in 2nd week of January but that she would put in a note to see if I could be slotted in early - I was pleasantly surprised on receiving a call to schedule during the first week of Jan! Edison and his installation team showed up on time,quickly replaced and installed all windows within the same day.\n\nOverall,very satisfied so far. I will update review over time based on how the new windows hold up.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Sree Nair"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I recently had the pleasure of working with Window World of Jersey Coast for my home\u2019s window replacement,and I couldn't be happier with the experience! The team was incredibly friendly and welcoming from the first phone call. Greg Rios,the design consultant,took the time to listen to my needs and answered all my questions with patience and expertise. The replacement process was seamless. The replacement crew arrived on time,and their professionalism was evident throughout the entire project. They respected my home,ensuring everything was clean and tidy when they finished. I was particularly impressed by their courtesy. What truly stood out to me was Window World's commitment to customer satisfaction. After the installation,they followed up to ensure I was happy with my new windows. I highly recommend Window World to anyone looking for quality service with a personal touch. Their amiability and dedication to customer satisfaction make them a standout choice in the industry!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Jose Guzman"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"From start to finish the team was professional and easy ti work with. The windows look great! Thank you","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Linda DeNivo"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The installation was done efficiently,professionally and neatly. Answered all my questions and showed me how to work the windows. They Cleaned up the area inside and outside. Very professionally done. George and his partner were very polite and courtesy. I would recommend Window World.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"christina frieri"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Great service and I highly recommend. Estimate and installation process once smoothly and quickly. Everyone was very professional and all my questions were answered high-quality products! Highly recommend.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Mark Kulikowski"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"This was the second time we used window world. They did a great job with our window installation and we were so happy with the job that we had them replace our roof as well.\n\nUpdate:My son accidentally broke one of the windows in his bedroom. First only the inner pane broke so the window wasn't open because of this. I called Window World after hours and left a message. First thing the next morning they text me requesting a photo of the broken window and serial number and they ordered a replacement for me with no charge because it's covered under their incredible warranty that covers accidental breakage. This company has quality service and treats their customers right. I'm happy with my windows. I'm happy with my roof. Maybe I'll have them redo the siding on my house next.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Mark Strus"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"This is my 3rd time using Window World. There sales representative is Awesome and the windows are top notch. Their installers are very professional and are very meticulous in there craft. I would recommend Window World to anyone wanting affordable quality windows.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"mark weidow"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The entire process of purchasing and installing new storm doors was very pleasant with Window World of Jersey Coast. The salesman Greg explained everything thoroughly,and the installation was efficient and neat.\nWe are very pleased with our beautiful new storm doors and would highly recommend this company.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Sara Ullman"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Great customer service. Excellent quality windows and great work. They are fast clean and professional. Overall great price. and great experience. I highly recommend them. My windows look great!!!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Madeline Tulipani"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Raina at Window World was very helpful and kind in solving an issue we had with our window. Highly recommend using Window World!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"sackylisa71"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Windows are well insulated and better than what I expected. The job site was left clean and the sales rep was easy to deal with and the pricing was transparent","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Michael Ferrelli"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I have great experiences with everyone I\u2019ve been in contact with at Window World from my initial meeting with Dan from sales to everyone in the office and the installers. Couldn\u2019t be happier with my 3 new doors. Thank you Window World! Highly highly recommend them!!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Margaret Palermo"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The windows are top quality,and the warranty can't be beat! The install was seamless with everything being done to my satisfaction. The team cleaned up everything from my yard leaving nothing behind. In addition,the girls in the office are extremely nice and helpful. My sister in Ohio,my sister in Pennsylvania,and my niece in Florida have all used Window World and we are all satisfied customers!!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Mary Ann Caplen"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I am very pleased with the work that Window World provided. The workers were very nice,helpful and professional. They did an excellent job installing the new windows in our home and look great. I would definitely recommend the workers at Window World.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Fernando Bustamante"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Great product,love our new storm door,worth the price. Service was great from sales to installation.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Anthony Cetta"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The installation was on time,seamless,efficient and clean. The installers were polite,pleasant and respectful,and answered any questions we had. Overall,an excellent experience. We recommend the product and the company.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Carol Silverberg"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We had a sliding glass door replacement this past week with Window World and it was well done!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Cathy Beck"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Excellent service! Dependable,reliable and cost effective! Came out explained everything and installment perfect!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Danielle O'Connor"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The installers did a great job,done sooner than I thought. Everything looks great,would recommend Window World to anyone looking to replace windows.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Bill Hands"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I would recommend Window World of Jersey Coast to all my friends and family. My experience with them was excellent. From the sales representative,to the account representative,to the person who schedules,to the installers,and to anyone else I might have had contact with were all very professional,knowledgeable,courteous and friendly. The sales representative was very knowledgeable and straight forward on pricing. Everything was explained to me and there were no hidden fees and it was all written in the contract. From the day I signed to the day of installation was about 3 weeks. Earlier than what was promised. I was actually able to make the appointment on a Saturday since my wife works from home. They were very accommodating. Installers were very professional,clean,friendly. No mess was left behind and everything was installed professionally in one day. Quality of the windows is excellent. No draft and windows do not feel cold. So the insulation that they claim is better than their competition,definitely is living up to their promise. Very happy with my purchase.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Andre Lopes"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I know replacing windows could be quite the endeavor,but when you have a company like this one,with such a reputable name,helping you out each step of the way,it makes your life easier. A big thank you to Doris who was the first person I interacted with and set the tone for the project. Excellent customer service from beginning to end and a job well done. Couldn\u2019t be happier with my new windows!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Jorge S"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"It\u2019s true \u201cSIMPLY THE BEST FOR LESS\u201d I am so very happy and pleased with the transformation on my house. Window world of Jersey Coast is the best ! I really needed windows and doors,but I was so apprehensive after hearing the cost and involvement of other companies and I almost gave up. My neighbor Phyllis had a truck pull up from window world and she said she was getting them done and she had prior good experience with them. Well let me say. Word of mouth by neighbors is a lot more reliable than advertisements! I got financing,everything was pretty easy. The job took two days only because of all the wood rot. They had to replace quite a bit. Everything was upfront no hidden surprise costs and they worked very hard ! Very polite and clean and professional.they also followed up and came back the next day to check all was well . I am so very happy looking out my beautiful windows. Good but old storm windows and broken half screens. Oh and I really love the crank window above the sink. What a blessing. I hope my review will help someone who is on the fence. I am very pleased.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Maryanne S"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World was very easy to deal with from start to finish,including having very minor repairs done when the job was finished. The sales rep John was very friendly and very thorough. Straightforward,no price haggling,the contract listed all costs with everything spelled out in black and white. Prices reasonable and windows look beautiful. Installation of 11 windows took only 1 day. I would definitely recommend them,very satisfied so far.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Susan Milne"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Very pleased with my new windows from Window World.The installers were very professional and courteous. Would highly recommend Window World to anyone who is looking for great service and outstanding pricing","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"dominick pirozzi"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I had a great experience with Window World,from my interaction with their salesman to the crew who did a great job installing the windows.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"cat turc"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Super product at the best deal!! John Gary,sales rep,really impressed my senior-aged parents,Nick/Mary. Their entire team and especially the installation men are exceptionally professional,courteous and respectful. One day install for 20 windows,a sliding door and a huge bay window. Bravo!! Keep up the good work boys,job well done!!! \ud83d\udc4d \ud83d\udc4d 5 \ud83c\udf1f","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Lambros Ioannides"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Great experience with Window World. Our installers were very professional,finishing 25 windows in a single day. Special shout out to Peter who came out next day to help with a small tweak on a few of the windows.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Terence Ng"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We had windows installed throughout the entire house from Window World in the past and was satisfied with the quality and aesthetics of it all. This was maybe 7-8 yrs ago and the windows are still in great shape. We didn\u2019t get new sliders (for the back deck area) because at the time,the existing ones were fine. But now it was time to install new ones. Due to the lifetime warranty,as well as not having to deal with third party installers,AND the quality of their work the first time around,we had sliders with built-in blinds installed. Price was reasonable (after some negotiation),installers arrived earlier than expected (in AM time block when I was told PM time frame,but that\u2019s okay,I was home),and installed a beautiful slider in two hours time. They removed the casing of the existing sliders,the doors itself,and the blinds with rack and hauled away. They cleaned up after and showed me how to use the built-in blinds and locking features. They did a nice,neat,clean job. The next day there was a nasty rain/sleet wind storm but the sliders stood strong,no leaks,or damage to the outside (caulk was neat,smooth,threshold of door was secure,measurements were precise). The built-in blinds are beautiful and a space saver! Plus it brings so much light into the kitchen now. I couldn\u2019t be more pleased with the entire process,from no pressure (free) consultation to install date - it took approximately 5 weeks from order date to custom make the door to delivery/install date (during holiday season too). It\u2019s been approximately one week since install and so far so good.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"P P"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"John Gary and the entire install team was fantastic","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Robert Bender"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We are very happy with Window World. They replaced 14 of the 20 regular windows in our home. The windows are well made and look beautiful. The team was very professional and worked neat and efficiently. Great job.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Nancy G"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"My experience with Window World has been amazing! Our salesman,Greg Rios,was very professional,polite,friendly,and helpful during the entire process. Prior to dealing with Greg and Window World,I had spent 18 months dealing with different contractors and door businesses. They either didn\u2019t call back or came back with an extremely higher quote than initially promised. When working with Window World,we were able to get exactly what we wanted,installed fairly quickly,and for the right price. The installation was done right before Thanksgiving,which was wonderful. The installers did a beautiful job,and were very efficient and cleaned up everything. I would highly recommend Window World to anybody that is looking for a beautiful door!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Peggy Schleimer"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"3rd time family homes have used window world. We have been super pleased with product sales. Installation and office I can't say enough.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Barbara Koestner"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World did an excellent job with installing my new window and patio glass door. All communication with the staff was dealt with in a timely manner. The staff was accommodating and helpful. The installers did a nice and neat job installing in one day.\nThanks to Window World!\nThe Brody Family","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Sally Brody"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Would like to thank everyone. Ordering,measuring,and installing was above line of excellence. I had called to more up windows to be installed,because of bad weather the following week. It was no problem.\nI had work done on front main window,that we purchased in year 2019. It developed a small issue,I called and had a service man come and address it. They stand behind their guarantee,to correct any issues that may accrue,of the windows they sell and install.\nI do fell a great difference and comfort with product. Thanks again.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Ed Wachter"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"This was my third purchase and install with Window World. As with all previous installs,the team was on time,polite,and neat and handled the install with ease. They went out of their way to resolve any potential issues and left my wife and I extremely happy and satisfied with the service. We already have and will continue to highly recommend their services.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Joe tortorici"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The whole experience of the windows being installed was awesome. I had 11 windows replaced and the job was done in one day! The installers were very efficient and neat. They cleaned up after themselves inside and outside. I love how the windows look inside and outside my house. What a difference. Plus I notice that it is not as cold in my house since the install. That was one of main concerns,when I decided to invest in new windows.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Stacy Cybulska"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We are extremely happy with the results of our new slider doors. The install was done to perfection. The doors look amazing. The pricing was really good especially when you compare to some of the big brand names,we are very happy with our new doors.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Suzie Rusak"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World had the most options for patio doors with blinds incorporated. I'll reserve full judgement on the windows and patio doors until the dead of winter and see if cold comes through.\n\nProcess was smooth. From sales person through installers.\n\nNeat clean installation and nice trim work done by installers.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Ray"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The windows look beautiful. Installers were professional and installation went smoothly. I highly recomment Window World","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Ladi Di"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Had my windows installed 3wks ago! Very minor issue that I asked WW to come back to adjust. They were very accommodating. Peter the repair tech took care of the issue and did an AMAZING job! Peter is an asset to WW. Thank you again WW for your quality work and staff!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Joann Palyla"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"From sales to installation,I couldn\u2019t be happier! Ken,my salesman,took his time & made sure I understood what my choices were. The installation crew came on time,were polite and respectful of my property. They showed me how each window and door operated. I will be calling in the spring to get my last 2 windows replaced and one door. I haven\u2019t received my electric bill yet,however I can feel the difference even on windy days. I am pleased with the quality of window world products.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"MK Clark"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The whole experience was great. From the first day when we received our estimate to the final installation date. Great communication,the office girls were great . The installers were respectful and cleaned up after. Extremely pleased with them. Will definitely use for other projects.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Anna"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"They did an awesome job on the windows they installed very good quality","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"4"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Jerome Goodsier"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Overall wonderful experience. From setting up the appointment,to the sales experience,to the measuring of our windows and shutters,right up to installing everything,it all went smoothly. Follow up was flawless as well. We love the finished job. Would highly recommend this business.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Louise Baldwin"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Had 3 slider windows and a storm door on our side garage door installed .... product works well and very happy with how it turned out. There were a few issues with parts and thresholds but Window World took care of them all. They were responsive at all times too. Also convenient to use within our HOA - they know the paperwork required etc and help to expedite things for approvals. Other people within our community had recommended Window World for ease of use and quality of product for the price....totally agree.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"LINDA E"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"we are well-satisfied from sales to installation process. The folks did a very good job on installation. They will be my go-to-place for any further window or door needs.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"emir gorus"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"great salesperson! great communication! beautiful craftsmanship putting in my window! On time! Cleaned up area! They give repeat customers special perks! An amazing company! Call them! Don't hesitate! I used them twice in past 8 years. Staten Island,NY","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Dee Garcia"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I had Window World a few years ago to replace my front windows and now I just had the balance of my windows installed. Such a fantastic experience from the salesman Ken to the installation team and office personnel. I will definitely be using them again for my door replacement when I'm ready. I highly recommend Window World if you are in need of anything to be done on your house. They even were so accommodating with my schedule for needed a Saturday due to my work schedule. Thank you","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Darlene Grodio"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window world is an excellent company to have install your windows !As a business owner myself I highly recommend this company!Come November they will install windows in my building where my business is especially after the job they did in my home!\nKen came out and looked at the job and explained to me what he recommended and gave me a price that was more than reasonable !\nAngelo and his team did an outstanding job on the install!\nI will be requesting them on my next install!\nI highly recommend this company!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"CHRISTINE Panzica"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World did a great job in helping us choose the doors and windows we wanted. They have an extensive selection. They came and installed everything on 11/4 and did a fantastic and precise job. The installers were kind and worked very well and efficiently. I highly recommend Window World if you ever need to replace your doors and windows.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Roman Shabatayev"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I had 13 Windows and 1 Patio door replaced. The installers showed up on time as promised. Did a fantastic job with the install and after they were done,vacuumed the inside and cleaned up the outside of the home. The windows are great quality and you cant beat the price. Highly recommend.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Gary Kalove"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Excellent service from the sales person to the installers. Everyone was very informative and professional. Work was done on time as promised and it is amazing how quickly they were able to get it installed. The new door is beautiful and the workmanship was excellent. They cleaned up so well it was as if no one even did any work. Would recommend them to anyone looking for windows or doors.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Teri Cruz"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Great experience the crew said they could get all the windows done and did in a timely fashion. Highly recommend window world for someone looking for great windows on a budget!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"joe horishny"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"So impressive the windows are beautiful it really made a huge difference in the look of my house. Gives such a bright clean updated look. I couldn't be happier,not to mention the professionalism of the crew. Clean up and installation was quick and done to perfection. Really could not be happier with this company will use them again for my French doors and all my windows in the rest of the house.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Heather Stone"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The entire process of installing a new French Door was painless and smooth. The door looks so good,and the price was better than anyone else. I\u2019m thrilled with everything and can\u2019t recommend Window World enough","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Laura Jewett"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I had a great experience with Window World of Jersey Coast!!\nThe team arrived on time and completed the whole work in less than 6 hours,including cleaning up in the house and debris removal inside and outside! Also they explained how to operate the new installed windows.\nI definitely recommend Window World of Jersey Coast for windows replacement!!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"NandoNJ"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World of Jersey Coast did a fantastic job installing our new front door! They gave us a very competitive price. The installation went smoothly. I would highly recommend Window World of Jersey Coast for all your door and window projects!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Robert Small"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"My husband and I had such a great experience with window world! 10 out of 10 from the sales rep Jack to the installation! They are also very organized! The install took 1 day for 15 windows and 2 doors. We couldn\u2019t be happier! Thank you window world!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Danielle Giarrizzo"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Hired the company to replace 11 windows. The entire process went very smooth,from talking with the sales person thru installation date. I had 3 other contractors give me quotes,and this company was the most reasonable. They kept me up to date on the entire process. The installers came on time and answered any questions I had. They cleaned up afterward and hauled away the old windows. This is the second purchased I made with this company and highly recommend them for anyone who is seeking to do some home improvement projects.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Dan Barasch"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Good experience from initial consultation to final installation. Salesman was excellent,really knew his product and options for replacement door. The installer was a real craftsman as to the installation of the replacement door.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Andrea Kadin"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World was fantastic. Price was a little more than I expected,but they did a great job. Sales,Measurements,and delivery/install were awesome and faster than expected. Delivery and install took place in a downpour. They arrived by 9 am and waited for a break. They finished at 9 30pm. Thanks!\nJohn Corry Short","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"John Corry Short"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I love my new windows!! The entire process was super easy,organized,and I wasn't pressured to buy anything. The price was the best I received and they include a warranty.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Y A"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Working with Window World has been amazing. From start to finish they answer all your questions and even helped with the HOA to get my windows approved. The customer service is top notch from sales to the office and the installers. Would highly recommend!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Jon Badaracco"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window world did a great job with our window install. From the very beginning of Dan coming out for the quote they were upfront about pricing,timeline and everything. They were prompt with coming out for measurements and scheduling the install. The installers showed up right on time and got the whole job done in one day. We are very happy and can notice a huge difference in the temperature of our house. We were having issues with draftiness and varying temperatures in different rooms of the house and haven\u2019t been having any issues since the windows were out in!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Alyssa Polimine"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The crew did a wonderful job working quickly and efficiently.. Very good clean up inside and out.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Marco"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"About ten years ago,I hired Window World at three different times to install insulated windows,the front entry door,and insulated patio door. I was extremely happy with the quality of their products and service. It was very easy to deal with their sales persons and installers at all times. Their workmanship was excellent. The prices were reasonable. I felt a significant difference in heating and cooling of my house. Because of my good experiences,I recommended Window World to couple of my friends who also hired them for replacement windows,and are happy with their new windows.\n\nBECAUSE OF MY PRIOR GOOD EXPERIENCE WITH WINDOW WORLD,I RECENTLY HIRED THEM AGAIN FOR VINYL SIDING INSTALLATION; AND AGAIN,I AM VERY HAPPY WITH THEIR WORK. THEY DID REALLY NICE JOB IN INSTALLING NEW HOUSE WRAP,3/4\" INSULATION AND THE SIDING. THEY ALSO REPLACED THE J-CHANNELS AROUND THE WINDOWS,SOFFIT,WINDOW SHUTTERS,ETC. THE INSTALLING PERSONNEL WERE VERY PROFESSIONAL AND EFFICIENT; VERY CAREFUL ABOUT MY PROPERTY; THEY LISTENED TO AND ADDRESSED ALL MY CONCERNS. THEY CLEANED THE SITE AFTER COMPLETION OF THEIR WORK. I HIGHLY RECOMMEND WINDOW WORLD.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Rajesh Desai"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I've never had any windows or doors replaced in my house so I didn't know what to expect when I started looking for an installer. My experience with Window World was excellent. Exceeded my expectations. Everything the sales rep told was exactly what happened from ordering to install. The crew that installed the two sliding doors were professional and knowledgeable. I bought the sliders with the blinds in the window panel. The installer made sure I knew how everything worked before they left. They also left my house looking better than it did when they got there. I have to replace my front door and will using Window World for that install also.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"K Miller"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World did an amazing job on our replacement windows. Everything went smooth as well as reasonably priced. The crew showed up on time and took care in protecting my interior and cleaned up afterwards. The communication with the main office was excellent. I highly recommend.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Diane Johnson"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Thank you,\u201cWindow World of the Jersey Coast\u201d,for an outstanding service and a top-quality job finished! We had whole house Windows replacement,Patio door and Entrance door with light panes job done.\n\nRight from the Sales Dept (Jack),Product Manager (Shane and his team),Office desk (Madaline),Peter (expert installer/troubleshooter) all these folks were always there when we needed them both before the sale done and after the installation done. They took care of all our questions and concerns with top priority and customer focus. Full marks to the Window World family for the professional customer service setup they have.\n\nThe last but not the least,head of the family Rimo who has instilled \"Customer First\" mindset within his office staff. It\u2019s his leadership that is clearly visible when we interacted with each of his staff members. Rimo is always there when you need him. He makes sure that he returns the call in case he is busy. What else a customer needs from the service provider?\n\nHighly recommend \"Window World of the Jersey Coast\" if anyone needs Windows,Patio Doors or Entrance Doors replacement. Great Customer Service,Top-Quality Installation,Trust and Cost-Effective products guaranteed!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Nilesh Kikle"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window world came at 8am on time as\nPlanned . They told me the deconstruction of all my old windows and installation of all my new windows would be done the same day . There were 16 windows in all. Two of which were double windows . The crew worked hard from 8am to 730 pm. They completed the job as promised same day. They Also were very cognizant of trying to leave as little of a footprint at possible inside and outside of my home . All debris from old windows was cleaned up and almost all the dust and materials was removed in the inside of my home . I was very pleased with widow worlds effort of installation and clean up. I\u2019m very satisfied with my new windows from a practical and aesthetic point of view. I would definitely recommend window world for anyone\u2019s window installation.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"josh wexler"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"My windows were old and draft was coming in. So i had basically changed all my windows (16 for the house plus 3 for the basement). Also changed the patio door and installed a storm door in the front door. Jack was very helpful and explained everything to us. I love the new windows and its much better and easier to clean as well the way they have designed it. Everything was installed perfectly on the day. There were some hiccup to install the storm door. They had to put some additional lumber and I was a bit concerned on how this will look but the guys did a fabulous job and it now looks as if it was part of the original door and they covered everything beautifully. Overall very happy with the product and the services","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Noor Ahmed"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Replaced 3 double-windows in record time. Messy removal,but my crew cleaned up beautifully. Professional is the word to describe Window World!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Richard Constant"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We contacted Window World after using them some years ago to make a replacement patio door. We needed a reputable company to replace our windows for our townhouse. We were happy with our sales person John and all he explained about the product. He offered us a monthly payment plan and that made it all possible. They worked with our association with paperwork and windows were ordered and manufactured in a timely manner. The install was great with only a tiny hiccup that was handled in a professional manner. We love our new windows. The rooms are free of drafts and most outside noice. All the work was done and no mess! We will always use Window World for our window and door projects.\nThank you to everyone there!!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Monica Kurkemelis"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World have completed the replacement of two front windows,and 1 sliding glass doors. The work crew were efficient,on time,and very professional. We are very happy with the work that was done to our home. A++++","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Lou Serio"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We engaged the services of Window World to replace large casement windows and a storm door in our condo. The job was handled professionally from the estimate to the final install. We received our windows in about six weeks from our initial request. The gentlemen that installed were on time and worked very hard to finish the job by evening. When they finished,our home was left immaculate. The windows and door are of superior quality and should provide many years of enjoyment. You will be very happy if you use Window World to install your replacement windows.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Karen Jaffe"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"As a first time home owner in a condominium complex that shopped around,I was so pleased to have used Window World. They had the most affordable pricing without sacrificing quality,they were able to replace everything \"like for like\" as needed by my HOA,and were professional and knowledgable without giving me a 2 hour sales pitch like other companies. Everything about dealing with them was pleasant and efficient; from the sales rep,to the customer service,to the installation. The installation was complete the same day (4 windows,sliding patio door,and front door). Furthermore,due to a misread,the crew accidentally took my storm door when replacing the other one,and not only did Window World put my door back,but they even replaced the door parts with the same type I previously had since they were disgarded in the process. They rectified the situation and did the right thing across the board. I would absolutely use them again and recommend their services to anyone in search of window and door replacements.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Kerrin Scully"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Very reasonable price compared to the many other quotes I have received. They installed all new windows and sliding doors in 1 day.\nI did have a minor issue with a window,and I called them and they had a service guy come out the next day to resolve. Turns out the issue was when we cleaned the window,we didn\u2019t close it back up properly,so it wasn\u2019t even their fault!\n100% would recommend and use them in the future.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Mark Bishop"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"First class company! Everyone was professional from the salesman Michael,to the installers,and Alexis scheduling the appointment. The crew arrived on time on the day of the install and the windows were done earlier than anticipated. I shopped around for prices and Window World was cheaper than the competitors. You don\u2019t get cheap work or windows though. We love the quality of work and the windows. I almost forgot to measure tech he was awesome also.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"David B"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I shopped around for a long time for my windows. I even endured a 3 hr long presentation with Anderson Windows only to find out that they were extremely overpriced!\n\nJohn from Window World was AMAZING! Answered all my questions and help me to pick the right windows for my sun room. He even assisted me with an AFFORDABLE payment plan.\nMy wife and I are very pleased.\n\nBecause my windows was custom made,it did take some time to come but I say it was worth the weight. I'm going to be replacing more windows in the future with Window World.\n\nPS. The only reason this is not a 5 star review is because the technician did not thoroughly clean the windows after install. But overall,I extremely satisfied!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"4"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Quinton Lynch"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We had half of our windows replaced by Window World a few years ago. We just had the remainder of our windows replaced along with 2 storm and 1 entry door. The salesman was knowledgeable and very helpful during the ordering process. The installers were on time,courteous,professional,knowledgeable as well as respectful of property. The office staff is friendly,accommodating and pleasant. I wouldn\u2019t hesitate to recommend Window World.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"L R"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I give 4/5 stars. The four stars goes to the whole team of window world. Great team,great quality windows,great installation. Only one star is off is for guy Greg who came to give quote at the beginning he is a sweet guy,gave us nice demo of windows and everything but he made two major mistakes where he put us in tough situations he messed up for calculation of contract where I had to go talk to owner get things fixed also he didn\u2019t include molding for windows in contract and again put me in situation where I had to call office and fix it so that one guy only put overall experience down but other than that Shane,rimo and installation team everyone did more and better than expectation so appreciate team..!!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"4"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Mishant Soni"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Great communications by the sales team,all delivery on schedule,no delays,installation team came on time,worked fast and installed both windows and sliding door with good quality,cleaned everything after work was done. Will recommend this company to my friends. Great job,thank you!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Mark Kotlyanskiy"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The salesman (Alan) was very professional,thorough,no pressure. He understood my circumstances and needs. The installation did not take long and there was no mess afterward. I am very happy with my new windows and when able,look forward to replacing a few more.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Dedria Panasis"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"From the start to the finish of this project,I have nothing to say but good things. From the sales rep and office staff to the installers,everyone was great to work with. I had six windows replaced. Wish I could do the whole house. The price was better than I expected and the windows are great! I would highly recommend Window World.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Elizabeth Vitale"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The installers went over and beyond to provide excellent service. We couldn\u2019t be happier!!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Lisa Tatulli"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Wonderful experience working with window world. They kept me informed the whole time. I was also sent a text messages when my windows were ordered and arrived. Install was clean and quick. Recommend this company.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Denise Oliveri Frias"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Excellent quality product and installation. This is the 2nd time I've used them for windows and have no complaints,both projects worked out beautifully. They are not the cheapest,but you get what you pay for.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Charlene Juenemann"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Love my new basement windows great job guys! Replace windows fast,perfectly clean,very respectful,great price!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Mary Ricotta"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The entire experience was great. We had a very good time with our sales rep. He was very knowledgeable about the industry and products. He provided a non-pressure sales pitch that was very transparent. Everyone was extremely professional and on-time! Actually they beat their estimation of window availability by a few weeks which was great. We replaced 14 windows in our house,and the crew that arrived finished the project in 8 hours. They put in the new windows,refinished the exterior trim,and even when needing to remove the interior trim,re-installed and re-caulked everything. Everything got tarped inside the house while they worked. The windows they installed were great and a much needed improvement to our previous ones that were 40+ years old. Their prices were the lowest around,with the best service we could have asked for. Its only been a few days and some of my neighbors are looking to use Window World as well. An easy choice to go with them again if ever needed. Thank you!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Kyle Miller"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Had a few hiccups.. I was originally sold a back sliding door that has blinds in it. To later be told that they don't make this size door with blinds in it. This was a huge disappointment especially since this was a huge selling point on getting all the windows done. They took the orice of the blinds off and we just had them install the door. I also was never spoken to about molding around the inside of the windows so on the day of installation they brought it up after installing 2 windows. Thankfully had some money in the bank after spending 14k. Besides that they did a great job kept it clean got rid of all the garbage. The windows are beautiful and work great!!!!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"4"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"MIKE B"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The installation and the whole procedure with Window World was exceptional. Due to weather conditions we had to reschedule installation which worked out to meet our availability. The installers were great and did an outstanding job.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Douglas C"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Excellent window install. The installers were punctual and professional. They were speedy and we were really surpassed how fast t they finished. I highly recommend them for their prices and the fact that my heating insulation definitely feels better now. Thank you window world staff","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Abhilash Buch"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The windows were installed quickly and efficiently.. Great job \ud83d\udc4f \u2026","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Hank Leslie"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We replaced many of our 35 year old windows,and had the box window in our living room re-sided. The windows are very nice-looking and the installers were excellent. They arrived on time,were very courteous,and extremely professional. The job was done in just under 8 hours. When they left,the house and lawn were clean. We're very pleased and are looking forward to lower heating bills this winter.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Bob Hoenig"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Recently we were in market to replace our windows and after shopping around we found Window World. As compared to other other Window installers,Window World is definitely cost effective (about 30% to 50% cheaper) with same quality windows. We replaced our Kitchen windows with Garden and Bay Windows and love the new ones. Their installers are professional and respectful of property and does a good cleaning afterwards. We will definitely recommend Window World to anyone looking for a new windows.\n\nBest features:\n* Affordable\n* Well insulated windows with several Energy Star certified window packages\n* Large selection of window types and exterior remodel products\n* Professional installers","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Ashutosh Sohaney"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Very satisfied with the installation and the product. It looks very very good. The gentleman that installed our windows were very knowledgeable and very good. They went up and beyond all the things that we wanted done. It was a pleasure to have work done like this. No mess an no problems.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Laraine Astuto"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We replaced windows for our home 14 windows and a patio door in total. We shopped around read reviews I think we got about six estimates. Some of the people who came were like high pressure type sales folks. It was all getting really frustrating and overwhelming. Someone told me to check the next door app and I did and Window World came up and had good reviews. So I told my husband let\u2019s get one more then make a decision. Dan Paone came out to our house on a Saturday morning what a really nice guy. We chatted a little he measured all of our windows showed us the product and explained everything to us in detail. It was comfortable and he didn\u2019t try to make us make a decision right away like the other companies did. We called him the next morning he came back to our house and we paid our deposit. The windows were installed on 9/26 the crew was excellent. It was a lot of workers I can\u2019t believe it got done in one day. Everyone worked so hard to get the job complete. One window had a crack in it the worker told us about it and he had already called his manager to order a replacement. They will be replacing it in two weeks. I had forgot that Dan told us how well they will clean up after the job. I was prepared to have to do a lot of cleaning when they left. We didn\u2019t have to do anything but move some furniture back in place. All the rooms were vacuumed like no work had been done hours ago. I would definitely recommend this company and we already have to one of our neighbors who asked about them after he saw how well they worked that day.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Casi"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Wonderful experience from start to end! Right from the initial explanation/demonstration of the products to the final installation of windows at my home,everything was managed professionally and efficiently. The pricing is good as well and I did not have to consider other options given the quality of their work and interaction. Would definitely recommend.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Harish Deshpande"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Installers were on time,and the job got done very fast. Things seem to be much better temperature wise in the house. The function of the windows are nice for easy cleaning. One of the windows was delivered wrong from the factory,but I was notified and it was corrected.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Jason Horvath"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"From scheduling a consult with Dan Paone,the presentation,pricing,signing the contract,and scheduling installation of brand new replacement windows and a new door,the process could not have gone smoother. I was updated often on the delivery date as well and happy to note that the order came in sooner than expected! The installation team was professional,courteous,and very thorough with the task at hand. They made sure that all debris was removed as well. I\u2019m so happy that my friend recommended Window World of Jersey Coast to me.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Sylvia Bush"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The price is reasonable and service is great. When one of my windows cracked out of the blue,I called customer service and they had it replaced in 2 months. Yeah it took a while to get the replacement window because it has to be ordered. I didn\u2019t mind as long as it got fixed with no question asked. I would recommend them to my family and friends!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Janice Ha Morales"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I am very pleased with the quality of the windows I purchased. The windows operate smoothly and quietly. The installers did an excellent job! They look terrific!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"John Beaumier"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The installers from Window World arrived about 8:30 am and started work at 9 sharp. After I took the man in charge on a quick tour of the house,showing him the windows that were to be replaced,they started right away. They knew what they were doing,and just went about it very professionally. It was amazing. By 3:00 pm they were done and cleaning up and packing up. The lead installer took me outside and showed me all what they had done,then we went inside and he showed me all the different functions of the windows. I was very pleased with their work and their on site professional behavior,I\u2019d highly recommend Window World. Also the price was just right,compared to some other companies.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Michael K."}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"From the sales rep,Dan to the workers,to the office staff,this place rocks! I had gotten a few quotes,but the thing is one of them was from Andersen Windows,as i constantly rec'd. flyers in mail. They walked into the room for the windows and stated,'sorry,can't do this'. What? Their receptionist was rude as was the rep. Don't recommend. Got another quote from a company & whereas their rep was awesome their price was way over double and they couldn't include a new door...? Window World is the way to go. Highly recommend. My friend got 24 windows and recommended them,thank you Anne! They are polite,professional and their follow up was great.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Laura Stephens"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Professional,quick & excellent quality. We had a large bay window replaced. Salesman was super helpful and efficient,had someone out to measure the next day and our order was filled within the timeframe they provided. Installers arrived on time and worked incredibly quickly.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Colleen Nieves"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"A very good user experience,a professional technical team,especially excellent in the details. It's been two weeks since the installation,and I feel great. The temperature in my home is kept comfortable,and it's quiet. Excellent,I will highly recommend it to friends.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Bin Hao"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I have used Window World jersey coast twice so far. Their windows are far superior than any of the others in my house. They are hands above their competitors and stand by their word of lifetime guarantee. Anytime there has been a problem,Peter has come to my house,always being fast,quick and efficient. He is extremely good at what he does. This firm is very experienced and professional. I would highly recommend them.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"iris Napolitano"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Very Professional,Great price,We were looking to have the final 4 windows replaced in our 1908 house. Window World came in measured the windows and had them installed in less than 3 weeks. Their installers were very Good. They came in and replaced the windows without any issues and they left the house as clean as it was when they arrived. I would definitely use them again and recommend them to everyone.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Edward Kane"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The installers were on time and very professional. They cleaned up all the scraps and boxes,nothing was left behind.\nThey did a beautiful job. I have three referrals for them,that's how pleased I was. I will have them back to finish off my remaining windows. Great job guys!!!!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Carol Hanes"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I am absolutely delighted with my new windows!\nI no longer feel drafts coming in from the previous glass and the new windows were well sealed! Installers came bright and early,worked efficiently,covered furniture near their work areas,cleaned up after completion of work. They then walked me through the process demonstrating how windows worked,proper cleaning and opening/closing to enhance the lifespan of my windows!\nCompletely satisfied customer,will definitely use them once I decide to replace more windows !","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Ruth Smith"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Love the windows! Everyone from the sales rep to the installers were very professional friendly and knowledgeable. Since I had over 20 windows to be installed I split the order over 2 years. Both experiences were top knotch. Workers arrived on time were polite and considerate and cleaned up when done. I would recommend window man to a friend.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Judy Knapp"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World has done a number of projects for us including our new front window,our bay window in back of the house and our front door. We are always impressed with their service,professionalism and the quality of their products!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Gabriel Rubin"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Spoke with Madlin and set up an appointment for this coming Monday for their rep. To Come to check 4 of my basement windows which need to be replaced. From the beginning to finishing the work every one at Window Workd was so nice and our Windows were ordered and installed. Everyone was profficinal and helpful. Great job by Window World!! . Thank you.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Moe Rastegar"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"This was my second time using Windrow World of Jersey Coast and they were the best. Had used them few years ago and so had reached out to them for my window replacement. They have the best team and good products. Explained me the options available for me and worked with me through out the process. Would surely reach out to them in future and would recommend their service to my friends and family..","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Umesh Pachpande"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Excellent service,professional installation and very clean. A couple of the windows when opened were not holding properly and sliding shut. I called customer service they sent a tech to adjust the windows in timely fashion with no hassle. Very happy with the product and service.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Carlos Gomes"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Start to finish the experience couldn\u2019t have been better. The crew who installed my windows were great.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Eileen DiPietro"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We highly recommend Window World. We had 16 windows installed and a Bay Window. The installers where very neat and organized. They installed all 17 windows in one day,before we knew it,they cleaned up and where headed out.\nWe are in love with our new windows. Window World is very thorough,the owner Tony stopped by mid day to check on job and office called after to make sure we where happy with work. The windows are very good quality,we could notice right away the difference in the energy saving,and noise reduction. Best of all the have a lifetime guarantee,so if ever needed we can call for a free service call.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Karen Bull"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World was a complete pleasure to work with,from the salesman John Gary to the scheduler and installation team they were very professional and did a great job. They installed 20 windows and one slider door in a Day without sacrificing quality. I would highly recommend them for all your window and door replacements!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Michael Chiofalo"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I called about a few damaged windows,a couple wete cloudy another had a broken seal and moisture got between the 2 panes of glass . The office staff was polite,courteous and responsive . A tech was sent out in just a couple days to take measurements and get info off the windows . The tech was just as Tha office staff was,polite and courteous . He took his shoes off as he entered,that was a pleasant surprise,as most contractors have to be told to remove their shoes and to not drag dirt or snow around the house .\nFast forward a couple weeks and I received a call that the replacement sashes were ready to be installed . Again the tech was great .\nIf and when I need windows ever again Window World will get the call and any friends or neighbors who say they're looking for new windows I immediately pass on the name and number for Window World !\nThank you Window World for great windows and an AWESOME warranty !","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Frank Bell"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World replaced all my windows more than fifteen years ago and I am very happy with the work they've done. Moreover,I have since replaced two window sashes and every time I called the customer service the representatives were friendly and professional and there were no questions asked. The friendly and skillful technician,Labinot,was quick to make things right. I highly suggest Window World.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Liviu Chan"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We were in a pinch to get a new slider and based on past experience Dan (salesman) was super responsive so I wanted to give him a chance on the business. He immediately got back to me and was out the next day to measure and get us a quote. Not only that but they had sliders in stock and helped us ASAP. The guys that came to do the install made the trim around the slider look even better than it was before. Great experience. I would recommend.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Ryan Krozser"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Very good experience with Windows World and i am someone who pays a lot of attention to detail. Pricing beat one of the main \"big box\" home improvement stores by about 25%. Installers were very good craftsman for both window removal/installation,aluminum exterior trim and cleanup. They carted away old windows and all garbage from the day so it looked like they had never been there. Highly recommended.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Mike Panter"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We chose Window World to replace a picture window and patio doors and were NOT disappointed. The sales person,office staff and installers all did a great job and I would highly recommend Window World to anyone.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Scott Long"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I asked WW to replace 9 giant windows. They did so on time,with admirable professionalism and precision. And they went beyond what would normally be expected of a business. Very nice,customer-friendly attitude. Overall,this has been a truly exceptional experience.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Jozsef Borocz"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I hired \u201cwindow world \u201c to replace all windows and doors in my house three years ago. Tony and rename kept their words as they promised. I was so happy with their work.\nNow I\u2019m even happier with their customer service and maintenance. I had to call a few times for broken things. Every time I called Kelly arrange earliest and convenient appointment for me with serviceman Peter.\nHe would come and fix whatever problem I have and check other doctors and windows to make sure everything is working properly.\nI think most important thing for a any institution is customer service . Thanks to Kelly and Peter \u201cWindow World \u201c has all that.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Themiya wasantha Galpotthawela"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We are so happy and love our new windows! Because it\u2019s a big project,I had questions and concerns but they\u2019re very helpful and very easy to talk to. The whole team,Jack,Kelly,Madelyn and installers,very professional. Thank you for the beautiful work!!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Lulu P"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World replaced 17 windows for us and did a great job and did it in a day. They also were able to fulfill several weeks early,so we got it done quicker than expected. Highly recommend.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Matt Rogers"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"i was very happy with the job that Window Works provided. I had my house windows replaced. the process was smooth from ordering to promise date of delivery until installation. I would recommend them and would use them again.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Marsha Butler"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window world replaced several windows in half a days work. We did have some minor issues during the install but they were able to fix them the next day. Would give 4.5 stars if I could.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Daniel Quinn"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Chose Window World because of my last experience with them. Installers were prompt,courteous and did an amazing job. Was concerned about the installation since woodwork around windows was delicate but the guys were amazing. Am quite pleased how good the windows look and work. Definitely will recommend to any one who wants a quality product and expert installation.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Loretta Bartlett"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We were exceptionally pleased with both the new windows and sliding door and the two gentlemen who came and installed them. They were friendly,courteous and professional.\n\nThis is our second time ordering windows with Window World and we went back a second time based on the great experience the first time.\n\nThe quality and pricing are excellent and the folks are all pleasant and professional.\n\nWe recommend them very highly.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Ellis L. Marples"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World of Jersey Coast really impressed us:outstanding workmanship,excellent communication,great value,and wonderful products! When we needed six second-story windows replaced,we requested quotes from a range of small businesses in our area. We had no doubts after meeting with Window World that we were hiring the right people for the job. We know who to call when we are ready to replace our siding!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Molly K. Eckel"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I had 7 windows replaced in my home. There were 2 men that came at about 8:45am. The old windows were out and new ones in by 10:30 am. They then took about 2 hours to caulk and put up the trim. They also put back the shutters that I wanted to keep. There wasn\u2019t a drop of debris on my lawn when they were ready to leave. Thank you,Window World. A wonderful job! They also made sure that I knew how to operate the windows!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Pamela Walling"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"What a wonderful company to deal with! I was so nervous about prices and installation. They walked me through everything and did such a fantastic job with amazing prices.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Lucille Contrada"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The service was great from the sales team to scheduling and then to installation. Everyone was friendly and easy to work with. The installation teams were great workers and did a great job. I would recommend them.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Denice Bloom"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Just recently I had instill few windows by Window World of Jersey Coast. I was very pleased with there excellent job .The professional cure did the job very good and clean.\nAll office employees are very professional and helpful .\nI am highly recommend there service to anyone who need new windows .","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Marian Zemel"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Very Good Experience. I had Window World replace 10 old wood framed windows in a old house I just bought. The turn around time was about 3 weeks. They came and completed the job in less than a day. The prices were the best out of 4 other companies I had come out to bid. They also did the capping on some other windows that were existing.\nI like the fact that the salesman didn't come out and try to pressure me into buying from them on the spot with a 3 hour presentation. It took about 15 minutes to get a price in writing.\nThe windows all operate as they should and there was no damaged moulding inside as they did most of the work from the exterior. Other companies were telling me they would have to rip off all of the interior trim which would have made a lot more work for me. No Thanks!! Im glad I found Window World and would Definitely use them again.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"J&L Cione"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I have been using window world for the past 5 years since i bought a house and I highly recommended their quality work and their honesty. They always give me a very reasonable price. Last order i did was the front door which was a special made order and Rimo was the one i dealt with and he told me it was gonna take 2-3 weeks since it was a special order and within 2 weeks and three days to be exact the door got installed. Their work is fast and clean.I highly recommend them for any small or big job.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Malvina Berdynaj"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"From start to finish,Window World was amazing. Ken,the salesperson,was knowledgeable and very helpful. The crew that came in for the install did a very thorough and great job. Their communication is excellent. Two thumbs up!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Malcolm Greenberg"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Beautiful,quality windows & doors!\nGreat staff from sales to administration to measurment & installation. We had 10 windows replaced + door & storm door.\nHighly affordable! Terrific service! I highly recommend Window World Jersey shore!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"B LG"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"\u201cWindow World Of The Jersey Coast,\u201d simply put:Is Reliable; Excellent installation Process; Windows are both Beautiful and Functional; Very reasonable wait time for the product to be custom made & ready for installation; AND,the installation crew was Efficient-Pleasant and Cleaned up after completion of the installation!!\nA Terrific Company to do business with!!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Barry Rosenzweig"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World was a great company to deal with from the first meeting to the install and ended up extending beyond that. They were so pleasant to deal with and that COUNTS!\n\nChallenges will happen with any business or service. It's how a business responds that makes the difference. We had two windows that needed attention,and Window World cheerfully came back out and stood behind their product,as promised! Trust in what they say and they will reward that trust. A+ operation. Well run!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Tony Monaco"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I was very happy with Window World,the efficient installation,the cleanup and removal of the old windows and trash.\nThe three men who serviced were professional and polite.\nI plan to use this company in the near future.\nAlso thanks Kelly for your prompt return calls and for adjusting the schedule.\nI would recommend Window Word to anyone.\nDebra Healy","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Debra Healy"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I had a fantastic experience with Window World of Jersey Coast. The window quality is great,the price was the best I had found and the workers were professional,neat and on-time. I had 5 windows and a Garden Window installed. What I like best is that twice I had minor issues,and both times I received a call back the same day I emailed,and a worker came out within a couple days to fix the issue. I highly recommend WW of jersey Coast! (note:not all Window Worlds are the same or run by the same people. My experience and recommendation of for Jersey Coast specifically.)","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Joe B"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Excellent as always. Sliding door arrived early and was installed 2 days later. Installers did a great job and left the area clean.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Michael B"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I just had a 5 window install in my condo 3 days ago. I cannot comment on the effectiveness of the windows in the winter but if they hold to the same standards as the installation I know I will be very happy. The installers came about 30 minutes early,no problem,started immediately,finished within 4-5 hours,cleaned the small amount of mess and were done! No complaints and yes I would recommend Window World","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"angela chevalier"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I had 5 windows replaced by Window World last year. They replaced a bay window with 2 double hung windows and some siding work to make it look right. Everything was awesome from start to finish. Alan was very friendly,super low pressure. The install crew was friendly,quick,and clean. Will use again!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"David Illion"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We contacted Window world to install new windows. Rob and Larry were very professional and went through all the options with us. Excellent customer experience I must say. They helped us getting all the paper work for the association approval. Their ground crew were also very professional,installed all the windows in no time and cleaned the place well.\nHighly recommend this business to anyone who wishes to get new windows.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Subramanian Ananthanarayanan"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I had 10 porch windows installed and can't even begin to tell you how pleased I am with the windows and guys who installed them. Troy and Hope we're so hard working,details oriented and professional. The quality and value for these windows were outstanding. I got several quotes,some double the price I paid. It has transformed the look of my home and I have had several compliments from my neighbors and my handyman. I will be back for additional services and will recommend you to everyone I know! Thanks Window World!!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Margery"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"They did a great job with the install. I had a minor issue afterwards and someone came out later that week to fix. The company was very responsive. Would recommend them to anyone.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"4"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Manuel Patusco"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Windos came in promptly,double hung windows came first,so they came and install all of them. Bay window came in two weeks later and was installed a few days later. They did amazing job with the windows and the outside covering of the windows. It just looks beautiful. The bay window is vinyl with oak trim around every window. It\u2019s beautiful.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Jeremy Ryan"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We have used window world twice. Once for our front door and most recently for 15 new windows. The installers were great and professional both times. We can already tell a difference with these new windows and love the clean look. My mom had referred us after she used window world for windows.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Lauren Territola"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Happy with everything from the estimate to the install. The price was great! Having new windows made our home look so much better.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Shannon Pelayo"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Installation was great. Very detailed in their work. Would recommend Window World to all my friends and family!!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Ralph Guidi"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Recently needed to replace my home with all new windows and was extremely pleased with the whole process! My windows were installed promptly and came out beautiful. Everyone was kind from the office staff to the installers. I would definitely use them in the future & refer my family and friends who need new windows. Thank you!!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Marissa Viteka"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We used Window World to replace nine old windows with new construction windows. Window World was used due to the great compliments we received from two neighbors who previously used them. Their sales associate Jack,was a pleasure to deal with. Both installers,Edison and I forget the name I apologize,were professional and went the extra mile. I would also like to thank Shane who was very responsive to an issue we encountered during installation which was no fault of Window World. The old original windows over time had leaked and damaged the ply wood underneath the siding. Window World will be used again in the future when our remaining old original windows need to be replaced !","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Shams M"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Windows came in early! Installers called and moved our day up and we were thrilled! They were extremely professional and neat! Worked their butts off all day and did a Beautiful job! Couldn't be happier,LOVE the Windows and will recommend to everyone!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"eileen simonet"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"timely,installers were very neat,covered floor inside,removed all garbage and the trim was done very well. Would recommend them to anyone for replacement windows","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"stephen meier"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I want to say Thanks for the most awesome experience with my window installation. Oscar and Angel were friendly,courteous and very professional. They even called before their arrival and were right on time so I did not have to wait all day. I am very pleased with my windows and will recommend to anyone! anytime! MaryKurian.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Mary K"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"This was a great experience. I looked at the competition like Pella and Anderson. Pella was professional but more than I wanted to spend. The other guys left a sour taste in 2 minutes. Window World from the call,to the sales rep and final the installation was professional with a great product and reasonable price.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Desmond Torruella"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Sales person - Ken Smith was very helpful - educates and helps you choose right product. Window installers were professional and completed the job on time. I would definitely recommend Ken and the Window World of Jersey Coast.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"H Shah"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Truly a pleasant experience from beginning to end. Larry,the sales representative was extremely informative and provided all options for the required job. The order was filled in a timely period and eventually flawlessly executed by Peter the window installer. Peter displayed true professionalism and dedication to doing the best job possible. Thank you Window World for a job well done.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Al Alleyne"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I had Ken Smith come into my home on the initial consult and his knowledge of windows,doors,and siding blew me away. By the end of the consult i felt as though he was right in tune with what i wanted to accomplish and the price was right on with the budget i wanted to spend so i decided to move foward though him and placed my order. When the workers showed up i couldn't believe how professional they were with laying blankets down where they worked and how fast they worked. They installed all the windows in one day which was very impressive and they custom built and cut on site the outside of the window frames. They installed the windows,siding,and doors with also explaining to me about all the work they were doing and it really made me comfortable and I like learning new things. They explained why my house was not energy efficient from what the last people did when they installed windows,siding,and doors before i bought the house. Now with everything installed I am able to control the thermostat for the heat and I couldn't be more happy to know I made the right choice in using Window World. I would highly recommend them.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"mikee mortgage"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The windows came out perfect and was a great price. When my fiance and I first moved to our new condo,windows was the first thing that was needed to be redone. The same day we saw our neighbors getting new windows. One of the installers,Peter Gorecki,greeted us and told us all about the company. Very kind,informative,and knlowdable guy. Peter was not pushy and gave us all the info we needed to get a free estimate. From then on,we booked window world hoping Peter would be the installer. Unfortunately he was not but he did come back to fix some stuff that needed to be redone.\n\nThe best part about this experience was Peter G remembered our conversation,almost 1 month earlier,and was glad we chose this company. Not only did Peter do a phenomenal job,but because of his customer service and skills I will definitely consider window world again and tell my friends and family of the great service. I give Peter a 5 out of 5 stars. Peter completed the job 100% and he went above and beyond and answered/assisted in an unrelated task that he had knowledge about. We had never heard of window world prior to Peter introducing him and the company to us. Great experience once again.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Scott R"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I only needed two windows replaced. Several companies I contacted either never responded to me or had a 5 window minimum. I was happy to find that Window World would replace two windows. I was very pleased with the overall process from the getting an estimate to getting the windows replaced. Everyone was friendly and the work was neat and thorough. The windows look great.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Arthur Hamm Jr"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"From the start,Window World was amazing! Sales didn't pressure us,their installers were on time and professional,and they did a phenomenal job. Highly recommended!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"David Zelingher"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I\u2019m so happy with my new windows. The installers were professional and installed 20 windows in one day!! No mess left behind it was amazing. I\u2019d recommend them in a heartbeat. The office staff was very polite as well!!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Jean Horgan"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Jose and his team were very friendly and courteous from Window World.The installation when very well and the clean up was great. I would recommend Window World to my family and friends anytime. A satisfied customer Maureen Glennon","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Maureen Glennon"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The salesperson (Jack) was great,and the windows were installed well. They cleaned up after themselves and for the most part it was a very positive experience. Two complaints:\n\n1. Complete lack of communication. Someone texted me to set up the install date stating they'd been trying to get in touch wtih me. Not true,that was the first I'd heard from them. The number they left wasn't in service,so I texted back and never heard back. They called my wife,set up a date,and we never heard from them until I checked with the salesman the night before. No idea what time they planned to get here.\n\n2. They took all the window treatments down and didn't put ANY of them back up. Left screws all over the floor in various rooms,blinds leaning aginst the wall,brackets all over the place. I've never had the windows in my house replaced so I have no idea if this is standard,but I'm not well-versed in the art of window treatments!!!! Super annoying.\n\nOverall a very good experience,though.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"4"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Rob Mackoul"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World kept us informed regarding the installation of our slider along the way. They were on time on the day promised and worked quickly and were professional. They cleaned the area and removed all debris when completed.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Marjorie Jodrey"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The windows was installed perfectly and with swiftness. Ever since they were installed,we haven't had any problem with them. During the installation no damages were done to the walls of the home,because they were properly installed by a professional. I recommend anyone looking for a window installation company use Window World.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Anthony Titcombe"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We were pleased with our window purchase. The installers were great and worked diligently to put them in. They left the area immaculate. I would highly recommend WindowWorld","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"richard pecoraro"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Windows and siding. They were great for the most part. The siding was contracted to a third party which had a few issues from damaging the roof of my patio and a few other things. Talking it through they said it\u2019s not their responsibility and were about to leave but I said I was going to call window world the complain. They were able to fix their damages before leaving and well nothing is perfect. A year later I\u2019m adding lights to my back yard and I get in a latter to go up and I find they never sealed well around one spot. I\u2019m curious now if I saw many mistakes at ground level (they all got corrected after pushing them to do it) and now that my first look at high level I\u2019m seeing this,it makes me think what else did they not do right and that I haven\u2019t seen yet. Windows 9/10,company talking to them and scheduling 10/10,my siding 3/10. Overall because of the issues with the siding I\u2019m going to say 3.5/5 stars,they really dropped the ball with the third party that did the job but everything else was great.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"3"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Manuel Angulo"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Installation went very well,without any problems. Installers were very professional,courteous,neat and organized. Everything,as stated in the contract was followed without problem. Would very much recommend.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Alanl Klayman"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Everything went smoothly as usual. This was our 4th time hiring Window World and we\u2019ve always been pleased with the product and labor.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Adriana Portune"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"When a Window World vehicle was idling for 10 minutes outside my home,I felt compelled to let the driver/employee know that he might have arrived at the wrong address. When I asked him if he had the right address,he said the address he was going to was \"down the block\" and his appointment was in 20 minutes. When he asked if I had an issue with him idling in front of my home,I told him I'd prefer he not (the carbon monoxide,nitrogen monoxide and nitrogen oxide from his tailpipe was damaging my lawn). He was clear that he had no intention of moving his vehicle and sure enough,he sat idling in front of my home for another 20 minutes,intentionally violating the NJ Statue that prohibits vehicles idling for any longer than three minutes on a residential street. I just got done my lawn reseeding project. Thankfully this is the time of year to do it!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"0"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Andy Gesner"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We had them do our windows,siding and install new doors. The work was excellent. We are very happy.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"John Collins"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I have used WW before and I will use them again. Fast,professional,neat and clean beyond belief...they truly know their job and are proud of their work. You can put new windows in your dining room and have guests for dinner the same day and no one would know you had major work done.\nWW is the BEST","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Francis Puccio"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The staff was very friendly and courteous from the office staff to the salesman and installers. The installers did a great job from the installation to the cleanup. We love our windows.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Luis Mojica"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Joe Adamo was very efficient and explained the process and the product entirely. The installers arrived promptly,were clean and quick and there was no evidence that they were there except for the new windows. Nothing was damaged in the process.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Sharon Forrest"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Had a garden window installed in Kitchen. Great Job by them. Window was custom built and installers did a great job. I called WindowRama first and the price they wanted was crazy. Window World did it for a third of the price.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Brian Rinaldi"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I am very happy with the windows and installation of windows and sliding door. Quality seems good and price beat competition. Installers were very detailed in their work. Would recommend giving this company a chance to earn your business","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Dirk Wabrick"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World exceeded expectations once again. This was the 2nd home they've done for us. The install,cleanliness and product is top notch!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Paul Lauterback"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We had a great experience from beginning to end. The windows are perfect and the installation was seamless.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Alex"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I used window world to side my house,replace my windows,install new gutters and put in a sliding glass door. We were very happy with the work they did. Their pricing was great,service was great and the product is good also.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Jennifer S"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window treatments are done pretty well by these guys. They're neat,professional and keep good work ethics. They're unlike other contractors that finish quick and totally forget the customer. I would use their services again and strongly recommend to others.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Prashant Prabhala"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I had window world install windows in my home 3 years ago. I had a problem this morning with the window not closing correctly and there was a big draft. I assume the window was broken.\nI called at 830 am and in less then 2 hours they sent someone to fix the problem.\nThis company is wonderful,great customer service,always very easy to reach by phone and they respond quickly.\nI highly recommend them,\nPS. The window was not broken,it was what i was doing wrong.\nThank you so very much,","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Roseann Rekulak"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I have used Window World for all my replacement windows and now my exterior doors. The installers were professional and great craftsmen. I highly recommend this company.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Robert Heinzer"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"This is the second project we worked with Window World of the Jersey Coast on. While this one was much smaller than the first,they were no less professional and the work was just as impeccable. The first time around we had a large scale project that included windows,siding and custom front door. This time it was just basement windows installed in cinderblock. The installers do immaculate work and went the extra mile to make sure the exterior surround looked finished,clean and new. I could not be happier with the results. Thank you!!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Angela Molinelli"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"2nd time using Window World,very pleased. Recommend highly","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"VedaAnn Rivieccio-Bruno"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The professionalism of this company is beyond compare. I would wish them all the best for the keeping up their good deeds. The installer Jose and his boss Rimo were too personal for having my 18 windows replaced and that too diligently in two days. Before offering them the job and signing the contract,I researched several window companies as well as independent installers,in the process I discovered Window World of Jersey Coast. I'm glad that I did my research even though I had strong several referral from residents in my community. Like other companies they didn't rip me off financially and compromised the quality of windows.\nI wish Rimo and his team all the best and my God Bless them.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Sid Soman"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World is a wonderful company. They Assist you in so many ways. I have only positive words for this company. I highly recommend this company to anyone who is interested in replacing doors,windows,roofs and siding.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"kathleen Nunes"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The windows (WindowWorld) and doors (ThermaTru) are very high quality and have made a huge difference in our house already. We live in an area with traffic; it\u2019s much guieter now. The house is warmer; we\u2019ve dialed back our thermostat settings. Since our old windows had many failed seals we\u2019re now enjoying the views. The best part,however,was the installation. Two crews,led by brothers George and Frank,took just a few days to replace virtually every window and door in the house. They worked very neatly and the exterior aluminum trim work/sealing is superb. We are very pleased with our purchase.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Russ Muller"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"My whole experience with Window World was Fantastic right from the start,Joe my salesman,the installers and office support. I could not get all my windows at one time but was able to what I most needed done and will be working to get my next set done by Window World with no hesitation,who knew you could be excited about windows I Love Them..Thank You Window World.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Abe Jr"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Customer service was second to none. On time,professional,not pushy with sales,accommodated our schedule and needs,and neighbors have all commented on how nice the house looks. No more drafts or cold sensation of the inside window when temp is low outside.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"J C"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The men came on time,They express what they were going to do,and they did it in a timely manner,they clean up and they showed me the operation and the safety option of the widows.I would recommend window world to my friends and neighbors.Good job guys\ud83d\udc4d \u2026","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Herman Reyes"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Here is the reason why I gave four stars to Window World of Jersey Coast.\n\nSale Presentation:Alan Rich presented his sales pitch and we agreed to go with Window World. This is a small project:replace two kitchen windows. Granted there was very little to no discount for this small type of installation.\n\nDelivery Time:We were told to expect 6 to 8 weeks to custom make the windows. From the time we placed our order and re-verification of the measurement from one of their managers,our windows were ready in around 3 weeks.\n\nInstallation Time:I received a call from John of Window World of Jersey Coast to inform me my windows are ready and it can be installed as soon as the next day at 1-3 PM. I agreed and made preparations (temporarily relocated the breakfast table and chairs and removed the blinds leaving the balance). No installers came after 3 PM. Called the office and spoke to John. He apologized that someone should've called me that the installers were running behind on a current project. He offered to rescheduled that day for 5 PM. 5 PM came and went. John called and said the installers won't be able to come that day,but can come on Wednesday at 8:30 AM. I agreed.\n\n8:30 AM of Wednesday morning became 9:30 AM as they claimed to pick supplies from Home Depot.\n\nProduct:The total time took two and hald hours. This includes the removal of the old windows and installation of the new windows. It was a two man team. Thumbs up on the professional installation\n\nRecommendation:Yes,but be wary of the installation time they give you. Don't accept their first installation date and time. Set your own installation date.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"4"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Stefan G"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"From the Sales rep,Office staff to the installers,everyone was great to work with. The windows are great! I would highly recommend Window World.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Srinivas Boddupally"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The whole team at Window World was amazing. I understand that they are the least expensive option but their service is better than the highest price providers. I would recommend them to anyone who needs windows replaced.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Roger Fagnant"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"On 1/9/2022,We had all of our windows installed from Window World,the prices were to good to pass up other companies wanted double or triple the price for the job so we went with Window World.\n\nWhen the windows were installed it was cold out and temperature weren't going to be above 25 degrees and on this day after 1pm the temperature started dropping but the installers worked and got everything completely and the windows look great also there wasn't any difference from the first window installed to the last window and I was impressed\n\nNow that night the temperature out side were going to drop into the low teens plus the wind was going to make it feel like temperature feel like they were in the single digits so basically it was freezing outside. So before the windows got replaced certain parts of the house would be colder/warmer than others so later on that night we went from the living room into the den,dinning room,& kitchen part of our house and usually it's freezing especially when the temperature drops but it wasn't freezing it was comfortable also mom when into her bedroom which would be even colder than the rest of the house and when the wind use to blow you can watch the vertical blinds move but now her room felt like the rest of the house comfortable and warm\n\nNow to wrap this up,Window World has made this experience easy for us from start to finish,the whole cost didn't breaking the bank to get done,they replaced windows all the windows in 1 day they were,also they were all professional and job well done,now our house is more energy efficient because we are not using the space heaters I don'thave to turn on the oven every morning to make the house warm so we are SOOOO SATISFIED with our decision to go with Window World\nAlso I can't wait for spring time so I can open all the windows,LOL\n\nThanks Window World,have a blessed day,from the Waters","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Pasqual Russomanno Jr"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"It took only a month between the order and the installation,the team came on time,was extremely professional and cleaned up everything after they finished. We also asked them to save some wood pieces from the original windows,if possible,and they made sure that all these pieces were removed without any damage to them.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Michael Gerstein"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Windows were delivered before expected delivery date. Crew installed all 20 windows in 1 day. Overall the experience was pleasant and windows were installed correctly with no complaints. I would recommend Window World in the future.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Reef Nut"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"The salesman was very through of understanding my requirements. He throughly explained the features and strengths of your product. The mechanics who installed the windows did an outstanding job. I am very pleased .","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Daniel Degerolamo"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World was awesome. They replaced all of our Windows and did a great job. The Crew was very professional and they cleaned up after themselves. I recommend them to everyone I know.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Big Raf"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We found it to be a most pleasant experience. The workmen arrived on time worked efficiently and with purpose. They were very polite and answered any of our questions...after the job was completed they cleaned up nicely.....would heartily recommend or use your company for future projects...","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Peter Quaglia"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Installers arrived on time on scheduled day were polite & worked to install several windows & storm door. Cleaned up when finished. We are very satisfied with new windows & door","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Thad Patterson"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"They did everything they promised and more. Everyone was professional,considerate and knowledgeable. No pushy sales pitches. They made suggestions and assisted in helping us achieve the best effect while being mindful of our budget constraints. The workers were careful,prompt and respectful of our property. We couldn't ask for more.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Patricia Garrett"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"We\u2019re so pleased & satisfied with the process from first calling speaking with John to make the first measuring visiting to St. Allen an incredible person that loves people all from the NJ office & meeting with one of the oweners himself Rimo when we went to pick out windows. I tell you speak about integrity. Everything he said to me it was so. Now the workers Jorge & his helper both great workers. These men worked till every window & door was done to perfection & then they did there own cleaning wow unbelievable. Lunch was definitely on me. Rimo you bless to have these guys working for you amen anyway LOPEZ family In Staten Island \ud83c\udf34 NY give window world \ud83c\udf0e 5 starts across the board. Oh & for the price was also & quality windows for an affordable prices.\nThanks Window World keep up great work\n\nLopez Family","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"4"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Wilson Lopez Broken Chains Recovery"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"They showed up on time.\nNo surprises what was quoted is what was billed.\nThe installers were very clean afterwards and did there work nonstop.\nI'm very happy with the job and the quality of the product they put in my home.\nI can't believe the difference just in the reduction of the outside sound levels.\nNice job!\nDon","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"DJCT1000"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Very professional great job looks great","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Colleen Dworak"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Great experience start to finish! I would not look anywhere else for my next project. From sales to office support to installation,every step of the way was professionally handled.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Pattie DiFazio"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"very good service. they came on time. cleaned up after they were finished and even washed the windows. would recommend","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"m s"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Fantastic customer service from beginning to the end. The installers were clean,efficient and answered any concerns that I had. Great job!!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Wanda \u201cabuelita4ever5X\u201d None"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Beautiful job. Best prices around!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Tammy McElrath"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":". When I scheduled the appointment I explained that it was for my elderly mother's home,but that I would be at the appointment,and I gave them my contact number. The salesman showed up an hour and a half before the scheduled appointment,which meant that my mother was there alone. The salesman left three prices for three different types of windows,but did not even bring in a catalog to show my mother what they looked like. Nor did he bring in a sample window as is the custom,to show her the quality of the materials... the \" estimate\" he left just had 3 prices written on it. It did not indicate if that included the labor,tax,Etc... would he have tried to get away with that if I had been there? Very disappointed!\nSalesman later called me to explain why he did what he did. He said he didn't want to\"bother\" my mother by showing her catalogs and the sample window. He said he had intended to do that when he came back and had an appointment with both of us. Well he didn't show up for the scheduled appointment,so when was he planning to meet with me?? Obvious Baloney!\nI previously had used windowworld in my own home,and the service and windows were fine. I had no complaints. That is why I called them again for my mother's home. But I feel I was disrespected by the salesman because he didn't come to the scheduled appointment... And I feel he disrespected my mother by not bothering to show her catalogs and/or a samples of what he wanted her to purchase from him. I feel that if she was not elderly,he would have handled the appointment differently. The salesman can give me all his excuses in the world,but instead I would rather he just say he's sorry,and then decide to conduct his future appointments in a manner that is respectful to his customer,no matter what their age,or how big or small the prospective contract estimate.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"0"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Cindy Defino"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"George and his crew were very professional and their craftsmanship was a compliment to their trade . I am very satisfied with their work,and dealing with the window world service desk was just as satisfying","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Peter Gardiner"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"They did a great job changing all windows in my house. Crew was very kind and polite. Answered all my questions.\n\nTheir windows so far have been great,they look amazing.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Giorgi Gelashvili"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Great work,installers left areas clean,everything went as planned,on time,great job","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Antonio DeJesus"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Great experience with salesperson Jack and the quality/craftsmanship of the windows installed. When minor difficulties,one of the owners Tony came out himself! Honorable company.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Kerry F."}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Window World made the whole process extremely easy,from sales through installation. A very pleasant experience,I\u2019m very satisfied with their work.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Michael K"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Great product,we were very satisfied with the whole job,the crew were very professional and friendly,I couldn't believe the clean up after the job was done it was great,I would recommend Window World of Jersey Coast 100%","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Mohamed El-Dalati"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I first used Window world at my home in North Carolina (14 Windows done) they did a great job.\nNow I used them in my New Jersey home (4 Windows and a full replacement front door and storm door) Great job N.J. Window World\n*****","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Paul Spalding"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"I am very satisfied with Window World or Jersey Coast.\nThe windows I got are better than any other company,the price was incredible.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Sara Ferrer"}},{"@type":"Review","reviewBody":"Windows put in very efficiently. Workers cleaned up perfectly and showed me hope to use the windows. Very satisfied with the product and the installation.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","